Summary: Columbus Georgia Witness Phones 911--Possible Downed Aircraft
trends: There have been 22 other sightings in Columbus
There were no other sightings in Columbus on or around November 28th 2006
divs: Sighting DetailsOn the above date and time, a Columbus Georgia citizen phoned the local 911 Center to report a possible downed aircraft. The events described in the accompanying Field Investigator's report outline the resulting later account given to the National UFO Reporting Center by a third party that had no knowledge at the time of the resulting ground search for the alleged downed aircraft. This inquiry was mounted as a joint investigation with NUFORC. Tom Sheets, SD MUFONGA, 13Feb08
